ConsumableAccountItem:smallxpboost.Name: SmallXpBoost
ConsumableAccountItem:smallxpboost.Description: Activate an XP Boost to gain Account XP boost points. Boost points earn [XpBoost.Self.Value] more experience for yourself, as well as give a [XpBoost.Team.Value] bonus to all other players on your team! If you are a Founder, you automatically grant a 5% bonus to all your team mates. The more players that use XP Boosts, the bigger the bonus for everyone!
